Market research indicates that automation-driven solutions now account for a significant share of new deployments, with organizations seeking to reduce manual intervention and operational costs. AI-powered analytics facilitate deeper insights into data integrity, threat detection, and recovery readiness, empowering decision-makers with actionable intelligence. This shift toward intelligent automation not only enhances resilience but also accelerates recovery times, a critical factor in maintaining customer trust and regulatory compliance.

